Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Camp David summit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040btb5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 17 Sep 1978
President Carter hosts Camp David summit with Israeli and Egyptian leaders. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.